    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"275920\">John Baez</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/229199-learning.3A-questions/topic/tensor-hom.20duality.20for.20commutative.20monoids/near/519379380\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks, Todd!  I'm glad you added it to the nLab, because it really deserves to be there.  I'm a bit reluctant to cite the nLab since it's time-dependent.    Maybe I shouldn't be.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You can cite specific revisions of the nLab, e.g. <a href=\"https://ncatlab.org/nlab/revision/tensor+product+of+commutative+monoids/8\">https://ncatlab.org/nlab/revision/tensor+product+of+commutative+monoids/8</a>.</p>",
